OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,7,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,8,     Funder the microscope. John checks
OL,9,     Fover a man who fell six feet on to
OL,10,     Fconcrete and may have complex
OL,11,     Ffractures.
OL,12,G2100 999: Emergency Call Out
OL,13,     FA devastating car crash leads to a
OL,14,     Fmanhunt for the driver and two
OL,15,     Fpassengers, at least one of whom
OL,16,     Fis bleeding heavily, and a
OL,17,     F13-year-old cyclist suffers a
OL,18,     Ftraumatic femur fracture.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
