OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FParamedics race to High Wycombe
OL,7,     Fwhere a handyman has fallen 18
OL,8,     Ffeet from a ladder, risking
OL,9,     Fcatastrophic internal injuries.
OL,10,     FElsewhere, 53-year-old Paula has
OL,11,     Fhad a suspected stroke.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Emma McMullen has her work cut
OL,14,     Fout trying to help a patient with
OL,15,     Fa challenging condition - and ends
OL,16,     Fup needing a wipe down! And a
OL,17,     Fpatient's mole makes it hard to
OL,18,     Fbrush her hair.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
